---
title: Herby Mushroom Pork & Bechamel Sauce with Garlic Crushed Potatoes
description: It’s here, the good-old bechamel sauce; it really is a favourite for a reason. The creaminess is offset by the earthier
tones of herbs and mushroom seasoned pork and a fresh garden salad to finish it off. Once you drizzle over that sauce it will all come together to form a delicious dinner.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

